  "detailed_description": "<strong>STREETOIR</strong> is a first-person / open-world / graffiti-centric / sandbox game, where you paint everywhere you want and whatever you want.<br><br>Roam a small city or take you time painting and hiding from workers on train-yard, or even try becoming subway bomber star. Try to complete side-quests or just have fun interactions with other characters and items. You also can try to master your painting skills, because game offers a huge palette and choice of tools and spray paint caps.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639980/extras/7516130dc9059efb4c098fc3ca6e55b7.poster.avif?t=1768127511\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639980/extras/7516130dc9059efb4c098fc3ca6e55b7.webm?t=1768127511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639980/extras/7516130dc9059efb4c098fc3ca6e55b7.mp4?t=1768127511\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Huge palette of colors <br></li><li>Different painting tools, starting from graffiti spray-paint ending with fire extinguisher<br></li><li>Several maps, so you can paint graffiti not only in city, but also in metro<br></li><li>A lot of interactions on the map<br></li><li>A lot of side-quests so you can interact with NPC<br></li><li>Freedom of action, do whatever you want and break the rules!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639980/extras/76d058c2dda65f51c4a52f0e9d100eb6.poster.avif?t=1768127511\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639980/extras/76d058c2dda65f51c4a52f0e9d100eb6.webm?t=1768127511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639980/extras/76d058c2dda65f51c4a52f0e9d100eb6.mp4?t=1768127511\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>STREETOIR</strong> is a first-person / open-world / graffiti-centric / sandbox game, where you paint everywhere you want and whatever you want.<br><br>Roam a small city or take you time painting and hiding from workers on train-yard, or even try becoming subway bomber star. Try to complete side-quests or just have fun interactions with other characters and items. You also can try to master your painting skills, because game offers a huge palette and choice of tools and spray paint caps.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639980/extras/7516130dc9059efb4c098fc3ca6e55b7.poster.avif?t=1768127511\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639980/extras/7516130dc9059efb4c098fc3ca6e55b7.webm?t=1768127511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639980/extras/7516130dc9059efb4c098fc3ca6e55b7.mp4?t=1768127511\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Huge palette of colors <br></li><li>Different painting tools, starting from graffiti spray-paint ending with fire extinguisher<br></li><li>Several maps, so you can paint graffiti not only in city, but also in metro<br></li><li>A lot of interactions on the map<br></li><li>A lot of side-quests so you can interact with NPC<br></li><li>Freedom of action, do whatever you want and break the rules!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639980/extras/76d058c2dda65f51c4a52f0e9d100eb6.poster.avif?t=1768127511\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639980/extras/76d058c2dda65f51c4a52f0e9d100eb6.w